Question: One image shows a yellow-cabbed truck with its plow at an angle that makes it look sharply curved and concave.

Reference Answer: True

Right image URL: https://bdn-data.s3.amazonaws.com/uploads/2010/09/1283601116_6f9a-1024x664.jpg

Original program:

```
ANSWER0=VQA(image=LEFT,question='Is the truck yellow-cabbed?')
ANSWER1=VQA(image=LEFT,question='Is the truck plowing?')
ANSWER2=VQA(image=LEFT,question='Is the plow at an angle that makes it look sharply curved and concave?')
ANSWER3=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER0} and {ANSWER1} and {ANSWER2}')
FINAL_ANSWER=RESULT(var=ANSWER3)
```
